HOUSE RESOLUTION 99
By Bulso
A RESOLUTION to honor and congratulate Sam Johnson on
being named the 2024 WILLCO Awards Male
Golfer of the Year.
WHEREAS, we are pleased to recognize and commend those successful high school
athletes who, through their magnificent exploits, bring honor to Tennessee and serve as
exceptional ambassadors of this State; and
WHEREAS, one such estimable individual is Sam Johnson of Brentwood High School,
an athlete of extraordinary talent, skill, and dedication, who has proven himself to be a
formidable competitor in golf; and
WHEREAS, in recognition of his success on the links, Sam Johnson was named Male
Golfer of the Year at the 2024 WILLCO Awards celebration; and
WHEREAS, Sam Johnson and his teammates led the Brentwood Bruins to the 2024
TSSAA Division I, Class AA State golf championship; and
WHEREAS, after finishing runner-up in district competition, Sam Johnson clinched the
Region 6 title for the Bruins by shooting a 6-under 65; and
WHEREAS, Sam Johnson epitomizes all that is good in today's student athlete, as he
has achieved a high level of success as a golfer while evincing great character; and
WHEREAS, Mr. Johnson's notable achievements are a source of great pride for his
family, his community, and his school, and it is appropriate that we recognize this accomplished
athlete; now, therefore,
BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE ONE HUNDRED
FOURTEENTH GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE, that we honor and
